{"data":[{"date":"09:56 02/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, \u0110T Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Oman t\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 1/8, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n bay N\u1ed9i B\u00e0i, \u00f4ng Said Othman Al Balushi - T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd L\u0110B\u0110 Oman \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft, sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Oman ch\u1ec9 th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Olympic Tokyo 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Oman c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Oman h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7. V\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi gian qua, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Azani \u0111\u00e3 thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Oman hi v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 Gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Olympic Oman ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 0-6 v\u00e0 0-2. L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, Oman ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, song n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\">U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi cho ASIAD</span><br />\r\nSau nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang trang b\u1ecb th\u00eam nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1907","checkdouble":"192528"},{"date":"10:38 02/08","title":"Nh\u1edd John Terry, Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/nho-john-terry-chelsea-sap-co-jack-grealish.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, nh\u1edd huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jack Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Chelsea-muon-co-Jack-Grealish-voi-gia-20-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jack Grealish \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Aston Villa l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish-172-190672.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</span>, Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Jack Grealish \u0111ang b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Aston Villa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Villa Park \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Aston Villa s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 TTCN \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Aston Villa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, nh\u1edd huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sap co Jack Grealish\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/nho-john-terry-chelsea-sap-co-jack-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u00ec ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Aston Villa nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Terry \u0111\u00e1 cho Villa theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, anh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Villa Park. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1980 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Villa b\u00e1n Grealish cho Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, HLV Sarri \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu The Blues th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u1ee5 Grealish, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1906","checkdouble":"192529"},{"date":"10:54 02/08","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Chelsea c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/sao-tuyen-duc-chi-ra-van-de-chelsea-can-khac-phuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 1/8 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD.</h2><h2>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb PVF t\u1ea1i H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 1/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Lo-dien-cai-ten-thu-hai-se-phai-chia-tay-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo\u00a0chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 trong tay 28 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0nh l\u1eb7n, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1eadt c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u01a1n tru b\u00e0i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang v\u1edbi gi\u00e1o \u00e1n ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Choi Joo Yong, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho danh th\u1ee7 Park Ji Sung, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL Tu\u1ea5n Anh.. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u00e1ch c\u01a1. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo sau H\u1ed3ng Duy ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u00f3ng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o ch\u00ed m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng Park th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o n\u1eefa sau gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018-168-192528.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018-168-192528.html\">\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, \u0110T Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar</span><br>\r\nNh\u00f3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Nepal khi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\">U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1905","checkdouble":"192530"},{"date":"10:58 02/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal mu\u1ed1n Klopp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/20/huyen-thoai-arsenal-muon-klopp-ky-hop-dong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal mu\u1ed1n HLV Klopp \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nabil Fekir t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Ligue 1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lyon. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ghi 18 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ligue 1 v\u00e0 24 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Robert-Pires-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-vu-Nabil-Fekir-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool. HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00f4ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 t\u1edbi Anfield.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Lyon nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Liverpool ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro. Khi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd, kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Kop sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Xherdan Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke City. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u1eefa. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-172-191696.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Fekir </span>khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Robert Pires v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal mu\u1ed1n HLV Klopp \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/Robert-Pires-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-vu-Nabil-Fekir-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Pires v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua\u00a0</span>Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFekir l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Liverrpool, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i sao qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc n\u1ebfu Liverpool b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. C\u00f3 Nabil Fekir, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Naby Keita, Alisson v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1904","checkdouble":"192531"},{"date":"10:32 02/08","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 Tottenham nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/de-son-heungmin-du-asiad-2018-ldbd-han-quoc-nhuong-bo-nhung-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng v\u1edbi Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 khi \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Son Heung-min ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. L\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 \"tr\u1ed1n\" ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n \u0111i l\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/De-Son-Heung-min-du-ASIAD-2018,-LDBD-Han-Quoc-nhuong-bo-nhung-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Son Heung-Min ph\u1ea3i xin ph\u00e9p Tottenham m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng chi\u1ebfn tranh n\u00ean m\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n nam b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tham gia ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1. C\u00e1c v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean nam n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Olympic ho\u1eb7c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ASIAD s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ASIAD 2018 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a FIFA n\u00ean CLB Tottenham c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng cho Son Heung-min tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n khi ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Premier League 2018-19 kh\u1edfi tranh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i Tottenham v\u00ec tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Son Heung-min khi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Tottenham nh\u1eb1m \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t. Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Newcastle v\u00e0 Fullham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung Min them mot lan nua bo lo co hoi ghi ban. Anh: \u200bFIFA.\" title=\"Son Heung Min th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1edf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n. \u1ea2nh: \u200bFIFA.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/de-son-heungmin-du-asiad-2018-ldbd-han-quoc-nhuong-bo-nhung-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Son Heung Min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn Fullham, Son Heung-min \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 1/9. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 xong v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp Son Heung-min trong hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11/2018. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Son Heung-min c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 hai tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i VCK ASIAN Cup 2019 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i C\u00e1c ti\u1ec3u v\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ed1c \u1ea2-r\u1eadp Th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t (UAE).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia, Bahrain v\u00e0 UAE.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-dien-cai-ten-thu-hai-se-phai-chia-tay-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192533.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi cho ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-iraq-rut-lui-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-18-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai-168-192516.html\">Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 18 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vtv-bi-ep-gia-ban-quyen-asiad-tha-dau-mot-lan-roi-thoi-168-192504.html\">VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD: Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1903","checkdouble":"192532"},{"date":"10:20 02/08","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/lo-dien-cai-ten-thu-hai-se-phai-chia-tay-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 1/8 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD.</h2><h2>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb PVF t\u1ea1i H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 1/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Lo-dien-cai-ten-thu-hai-se-phai-chia-tay-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo\u00a0chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 trong tay 28 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0nh l\u1eb7n, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1eadt c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u01a1n tru b\u00e0i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang v\u1edbi gi\u00e1o \u00e1n ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Choi Joo Yong, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho danh th\u1ee7 Park Ji Sung, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL Tu\u1ea5n Anh.. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u00e1ch c\u01a1. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo sau H\u1ed3ng Duy ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u00f3ng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o ch\u00ed m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng Park th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o n\u1eefa sau gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018-168-192528.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018-168-192528.html\">\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, \u0110T Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar</span><br>\r\nNh\u00f3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Nepal khi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\">U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1902","checkdouble":"192533"},{"date":"10:31 02/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh AIK Solna vs Nordsjaelland 00h00 ng\u00e0y 3/8 (Europa League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/nhan-dinh-aik-solna-vs-nordsjaelland-00h00-ngay-38-europa-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>AIK Solna vs Nordsjaelland l\u00fac 00h00 ng\u00e0y 3/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Europa League/c\u00fap C2 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh AIK Solna vs Nordsjaelland 00h00 ng\u00e0y 38 Europa League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh AIK Solna vs Nordsjaelland 00h00 ng\u00e0y 38 Europa League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/AIK-Solna-vs-Nordsjaelland.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">AIK Solna vs Nordsjaelland</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> AIK Solna vs Nordsjaelland: 1-1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, AIK Solna \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd bung s\u1ee9c cho v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 Europa League nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Rikard Norling \u0111\u00e3 thua Nordsjaelland 0-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, AIK Solna bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam nay \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd. Song CLB\u00a0Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn \u1edf h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, ngo\u00e0i m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t t\u00e2n binh Brommapojkarna \u1edf gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, AIK Solna ch\u01b0a ghi n\u1ed5i qu\u00e1 1 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a AIK Solna kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nordsjaelland. \u0110\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nordsjaelland \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 11 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0nh trang m\u00e0 Nordsjaelland chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam nay l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 3-0\u00a0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u1ecd gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi. V\u1edbi \u01b0u th\u1ebf 1 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1o ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1eeba l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam nay \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ AIK Solna (3-1-4-2): Linner - Milosevic, Jansson, Karlsson - Adu - Sundgren, Larsson, Olsson, Lindkvist - Stefanelli, Elyounoussi.<br>\r\n+ Nordsjaelland (3-4-3): Larsen - Skovgraard, Jenssen, Nelsson - Bartolec, Andersen, Christensen, Pedersen - Olsen, Damsgaard, Jensen.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1901","checkdouble":"192534"},{"date":"11:07 02/08","title":"D\u00f9ng doping, sao kh\u1ee7ng Premier League nh\u1eadn \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2... 18 th\u00e1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dung-doping-sao-khung-premier-league-nhan-an-treo-gio-18-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal v\u00e0 Man City \u2013 Samir Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5m.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNasri b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua, Nasri \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 6 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng doping. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, UEFA c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e2ng m\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1t l\u00ean t\u1edbi 18 th\u00e1ng cho c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sevilla d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1m t\u1ea1i Los Angeles v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 12/2016 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong m\u1ee5c c\u1ea5m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng may \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb C\u01a1 quan ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ed1ng doping tu\u00fdt c\u00f2i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng doping \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb\" title=\"Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/dung-doping-sao-khung-premier-league-nhan-an-treo-gio-18-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng doping \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sevilla gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb Man City s\u1edbm thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. T\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 8/2017, anh gia nh\u1eadp CLB Antalyaspor \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 8 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 do tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c \u00e1n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 18 th\u00e1ng treo gi\u00f2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a UEFA, m\u1ee9c \u00e1n n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7/2017. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a Nasri s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m nay. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o d\u00f9 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, b\u1edfi Nasri l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n cho c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u1edf Premier League, v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i La Liga. Vi\u1ec7c&nbsp;Samir Nasri b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 18 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng doping s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, b\u1edfi n\u0103m nay anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 31.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tuyen-thu-phap-khoe-sieu-xe-ferrari-khi-tro-lai-hoi-quan-cung-man-city-188-192477.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/tuyen-thu-phap-khoe-sieu-xe-ferrari-khi-tro-lai-hoi-quan-cung-man-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/tuyen-thu-phap-khoe-sieu-xe-ferrari-khi-tro-lai-hoi-quan-cung-man-city-188-192477.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p khoe si\u00eau xe Ferrari khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng Man City</span><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Mendy m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng Les Bleus b\u1eb1ng Ferrari F2X m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng ch\u00f3e.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vua-co-thay-moi-bellerin-da-len-tieng-che-bai-wenger-172-192519.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/vua-co-thay-moi-bellerin-da-len-tieng-che-bai-wenger.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vua-co-thay-moi-bellerin-da-len-tieng-che-bai-wenger-172-192519.html\">V\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi, Bellerin \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00ea bai Wenger</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;Arsenal l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo; &ndash; h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin ch\u00ea bai Wenger, sau kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi Emery.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1900","checkdouble":"192535"},{"date":"11:18 02/08","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 2/8: M.U c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang Barca \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/ngay-hom-nay-28.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (2/8). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM.U c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang\u00a0Barca \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mina\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 28, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 28, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/muc-tieu-cua-mu-tiet-lo-bi-messi-va-suarez-bat-nat-o-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nTuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean M.U Matt Judge \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn Camp Nou \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia c\u1ee7a Barca Yerry Mina. Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p \u00f4ng Matt Judge \u1edf M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea9n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mua ngay m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf. \u00d4ng Matt Judge \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u00e0 Mourinho ch\u1ecdn Matt Judge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Camp Nou \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mina l\u1eabn ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 M.U s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. M.U \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau mua s\u1eafm tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld v\u00e0 Harry Maguire. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Tottenham \u0111\u00f2i t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 2 Leicester \u0111\u00f2i 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ph\u00e1 k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c mua Oblak</h2>\r\nSau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh Pickford v\u00e0 Schmeichel, Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ednh t\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Jan Oblak v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid (kho\u1ea3ng 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng). N\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, Oblak s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alisson, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0, \u00e9p The Blues ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n m\u00ecnh cho Real n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<h2>Juventus v\u00e0 Milan ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 3 ng\u00f4i sao</h2>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec c\u00e1c v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Caldara, Bonucci v\u00e0 Higuain c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 li\u00ean quan c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Higuain gia nh\u1eadp Milan d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 Milan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1ee9t n\u1ebfu tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 36 tri\u1ec7u n\u1eefa. Caldara v\u00e0 Bonucci \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao \u0111\u1ed5i ngang gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 Juve \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho kh\u00f4ng c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i Caldara v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Bonucci.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 28 MU c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang Barca \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mina  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 28 MU c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang Barca \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mina  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-28-MU-cu-nguoi-sang-Barca-dam-phan-mua-Mina--hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Modric</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Inter \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Modric</h2>\r\nSerie A \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng l\u00f4i k\u00e9o th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1eefa khi Inter mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Luka Modric. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Real Madrid l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. Ph\u00eda nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd Modric l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn chuy\u1ec3n sang Inter thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Real.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/inter-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-luka-modric-184-192453.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham mua \u201ch\u00e0ng l\u1edfm\u201d</h2>\r\nTottenham v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u1eeba qua HLV Pochettino ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cook c\u1ee7a Bournemouth. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u201ch\u1ea1t ti\u00eau\u201d Premier League quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.\r\n<h2>Giroud s\u1eafp b\u1ecb Chelsea \u0111\u1ea9y ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</h2>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Giroud t\u1ea1i Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Goal, hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Giroud kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh n\u00ean \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Marseille.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1899","checkdouble":"192539"},{"date":"11:21 02/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/2/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mina l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0208-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mina nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMU mua Yerry Mina l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/11/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Bom t\u1ea5n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nMU mua Yerry Mina l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng M.U s\u1ebd chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Toni Kroos v\u00e0 Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ea1i gia Italia ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha Matteo Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a M.U. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1eabn \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Mateo Kovacic quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp M.U v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i do Mourinho x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Harry Maguire</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maguire\" title=\"Maguire\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/hlv-leicester-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-mu-chieu-mo-maguire.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U kh\u00f4ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU n\u1ebfu Mourinho ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zidane\" title=\"Zidane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ngay-hom-nay-18.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Mourinho d\u1eabn d\u1eaft M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zidane d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU thay Mourinho, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Yerry Mina n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU quan t\u00e2m?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca hay ra \u0111i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal, Everton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Maros Rojo c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mina c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1898","checkdouble":"192540"},{"date":"07:16 02/08","title":"HLV Sarri h\u1ee9a tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng sao tr\u1ebb 17 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-sarri-hua-trong-dung-sao-tre-17-tuoi-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi. T\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 17 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. </h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hudson-Odoi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, U17 Anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Callum Hudson-Odoi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 2000 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Antonio Conte trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Hudson-Odoi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Chelsea. \u0110\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Arsenal t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup, sao tr\u1ebb ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 18 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. D\u00f9 Chelsea th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 6-5 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m (h\u00f2a 1-1 sau 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh), Hudson-Odoi v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ng\u1ee3i khen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u1ee3i khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u1ee3i khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/tien-dao-Hudson-Odoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hudson-Odoi ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01a1i ch\u1ebfch v\u1ec1 b\u00ean tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Chelsea, Hudson-Odoi \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Hector Bellerin c\u1ee7a Arsenal kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh. Anh c\u00f2n ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty song Alvaro Morata \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri t\u1eb7ng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn, Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ef9 t\u1eeb. \u00d4ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho sao tr\u1ebb 17 tu\u1ed5i ra s\u00e2n trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. &ldquo;Hudson-Odoi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian&rdquo;, Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Hudson-Odoi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t, r\u1ea5t tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (\u0111\u1ed9i 1 Chelsea) trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri da khong the co duoc Golovin trong doi hinh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chelsea-muon-mua-Lewandowski-cua-Bayern-Munich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u1ee3i khen</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlvaro Morata l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ecb anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1. \u0110ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin The Blues d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea9y ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 Morata c\u00f3 thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin hay kh\u00f4ng&rdquo;, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i th\u00eam. &ldquo;D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 Morata.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Arsenal 1-1 (pen 6-5) Chelsea:</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/2/Arsenal-vs-Chelsea_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-muon-da-tan-cong-phai-cho-kante-172-192492.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng? Ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd Kante</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mot-lat-cat-ve-maurizio-sarri-buoc-ra-anh-sang-phia-ben-kia-suon-doc-389-192482.html\">M\u1ed9t l\u00e1t c\u1eaft v\u1ec1 Maurizio Sarri: B\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nham-kovacic-trong-truong-hop-khong-co-duoc-ramsey-172-192463.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ee5 Aaron Ramsey</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/psg-chua-tu-bo-kante-172-192456.html\">PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf tham v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu sao s\u00e1ng Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barkley-quyet-tim-lai-vi-tri-o-chelsea-172-192452.html\">Barkley quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1897","checkdouble":"192509"},{"date":"07:28 02/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (2/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-282018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-