order:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 2/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u00e1n Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet.</strong> Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a The Kop \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb M.U. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chuy\u1ec3n sang Manchester United. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi gian qua. Nh\u01b0ng Kovacic kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi M.U v\u00ec c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 28 Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb M h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 28 Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb M h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-28-Sao-that-sung-cua-Real-khuoc-tu-M-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra tung t\u00edch c\u1ee7a sao M.U bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. </strong>Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1eb1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ea1i gia Italia ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha Matteo Darmian.</strong> Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a M.U. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1eabn \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o\u201d x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Milan ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.</strong> Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Rossoneri ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Gonzalo Higuain\" title=\"tien dao Gonzalo Higuain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Vuot-mat-AC-Milan,-Chelsea-muon-mua-Gonzalo-Higuain-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Higuain s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Sarri h\u1ee9a tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng sao tr\u1ebb 17 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Chelsea. </strong>Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi. T\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 17 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. </strong>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Shaka Hislop m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean Everton. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y n\u00ean tr\u00e1nh xa trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Man United n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng h\u1edb gi\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nPires d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</strong> Robert Pires d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Alexandre Lacazette. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tin \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng 20 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1895","checkdouble":"192511"},{"date":"08:22 02/08","title":"G\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea v\u1eabn b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u1ee5 \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/gui-loi-de-nghi-sieu-khung-chelsea-van-bi-tu-choi-vu-zaha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Danny Drinkwater song Crystal Palace \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Zaha</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard v\u00e0 Willian l\u00e0 2 trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. M.U \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Willian, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Chelsea-muon-mua-Wilfried-Zaha-voi-loi-de-nghi-cuc-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Zaha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hazard</span>, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Willian, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef Hazard v\u00e0 Willian, Chelsea c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Theo Mirror v\u00e0 ESPN, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Wilfried Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Zaha l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Palace. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh, Zaha s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Crystal Palace t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Zaha cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Danny Drinkwater song Crystal Palace \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea v\u1eabn b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea v\u1eabn b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/1/Gui-loi-de-nghi-sieu-khung,-Chelsea-van-bi-tu-choi-vu-hang-thai-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Crystal Palace t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Zaha cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra \u0111i, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Zaha \u1edf l\u1ea1i. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a\u00a0Chelsea ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Palace ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t, thay v\u00ec nh\u1eadn 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 Drinkwater.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCrystal Palace mu\u1ed1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9ng kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Ngo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u sao M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Palace nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Man City c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Zaha, song l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mahrez.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1894","checkdouble":"192512"},{"date":"08:41 02/08","title":"Barca nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/barca-nhan-don-dau-vu-rabiot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi PSG.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Rabiot</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho ra \u0111i, Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Rafinha v\u00e0 Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng. HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/PSG-chan-duong-Barca-mua-Adrien-Rabiot-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Rabiot\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, song PSG v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. C\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng Rabiot mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi PSG do lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Tuchel.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh s\u1ee3 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb sau khi c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Julian Draxler \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG b\u00e1n Raniot, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho anh m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng. D\u00f9 PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-cho-them-7-ngay-de-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-psg-180-192423.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca v\u1eabn ch\u1edd th\u00eam 7 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Rabiot</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, sau \u0111\u00f3 Barca s\u1ebd v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean,\u00a0trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 Rabiot.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rabiot s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"PSG ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/barca-nhan-don-dau-vu-rabiot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rabiot s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i l\u00e0 b\u1edfi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng m\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam\u00a04 n\u0103m k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi Rabiot nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 490.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y t\u1eeb PSG, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 ngay \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf l\u1ea1i thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1893","checkdouble":"192514"}]}